Class FitBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window
          • java.awt.Dialog
            • javax.swing.JDialog
              • org.opensourcephysics.tools.FunctionTool
                • org.opensourcephysics.tools.FitBuilder

  • public class FitBuilder
extends FunctionTool
    This is a FunctionTool used by DatasetCurveFitter to build, save and load custom fit functions. Some methods are tailored for use with DataTool since that is its main application.
    See Also:
